Here are the wiring connections for
traffic control system using the 
**VSD Squadron Mini** :

1. HC-SR04 VCC → 5V (VSD Squadron Mini)  
2. HC-SR04 GND → GND (VSD Squadron Mini)  
3. HC-SR04 Trig → PC0 (VSD Squadron Mini)  
4. HC-SR04 Echo → PC1 (VSD Squadron Mini)  
5. Red LED (+) → PC2 (VSD Squadron Mini)  
6. Green LED (+) → PC3 (VSD Squadron Mini)  
7. LED GND (-) → GND (via 220Ω resistor)
